      <title>韩国住院医生数量因与尹某的矛盾而大幅下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/south-korea-resident-doctors-intake-plunges-amid-rift-with-yoon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国住院医生的招聘数量跌至多年来的最低水平，加剧了医生短缺的问题，导致政府与医生之间产生矛盾，而总统尹锡烈实施的现已中止的戒严令使情况变得更糟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/south-korea-resident-doctors-intake-plunges-amid-rift-with-yoon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 10:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
